## JavaScript Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph "script.js"
        A[DOMContentLoaded] --> B[animateOnScroll()]
        A --> C[setupMobileMenu()]
        A --> D[setupProductCards()]
        A --> E[setupFormValidation()]
        
        B --> F[IntersectionObserver]
        B --> G[Animated Elements\n.carte-produit\n.section-apropos\n.hero]
        
        C --> H[menuToggle click handler]
        C --> I[nav.classList.toggle active]
        C --> J[body.classList.toggle menu-open]
        
        D --> K[mouseenter/mouseleave\non carte-produit]
        D --> L[transform translateY]
        D --> M[boxShadow changes]
        
        E --> N[formulaire-contact submit]
        E --> O[Validation Fields]
        O --> P[nom required]
        O --> Q[email required + format]
        O --> R[sujet required]
        O --> S[message required]
        E --> T[showError()]
        E --> U[clearErrors()]
        E --> V[isValidEmail() regex]
        
        E --> W[Formspree.io POST]
    end
    
    subgraph "Utility Functions"
        X[addClass()]
        Y[removeClass()]
        Z[toggleClass()]
    end
```

## SEO & Metadata Structure

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph "SEO Elements"
        A[sitemap.xml] --> B[URL entries x11]
        B --> C[index.html priority 1.0]
        B --> D[a-propos.html priority 0.8]
        B --> E[contact.html priority 0.8]
        B --> F[produits/*.html priority 0.6]
        
        G[robots.txt] --> H[User-agent: *]
        G --> I[Allow: /]
        G --> J[Sitemap reference]
        
        K[llms.txt] --> L[User-agent: *]
        K --> M[Disallow: /]
        K --> N[LLM-Allowed: false]
        
        O[Meta Tags] --> P[charset UTF-8]
        O --> Q[viewport responsive]
        O --> R[title unique per page]
    end
    
    subgraph "Social & Analytics"
        S[Google Search Console\n2 verification files]
        T[Facebook Group Link]
        U[Instagram Link placeholder]
    end
```

